warning[L0013]: This `when` only unwraps `ok` and re-propagates `err` вҖ” that's what `try` does.
   в”Ӯ
   в”ңв”Җрңұ¶ help: rewrite as `try <binding> = <subject>` followed by the success body; `try` short-circuits on `err`, so the error arm goes away.
